---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro'
import Header from '../components/landing/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/landing/Footer.astro'
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Terms of Service - Chat2Note"
  description="Terms of service for Chat2Note browser extension - understand your rights and responsibilities when using our service."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: October 4, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            By installing and using Chat2Note ("the Extension"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the Extension.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Chat2Note is a browser extension that allows users to export conversations from AI chat platforms (including ChatGPT, Claude, DeepSeek, Gemini, Kimi, Yuanbao, Doubao, and Grok) to various formats and destinations. All processing is performed locally in your browser.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">3. License and Usage Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Subject to your compliance with these Terms, we grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use Chat2Note for personal or commercial purposes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            You may:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Use the Extension for any lawful purpose</li>
            <li>Export conversations from supported AI platforms</li>
            <li>Modify the source code for personal use (subject to the project's open source license)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            You are responsible for:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Ensuring that your use of the Extension complies with the terms of service of the AI chat platforms you use (ChatGPT, Claude, DeepSeek, Gemini, Kimi, Yuanbao, Doubao, Grok, etc.)</li>
            <li>Maintaining the confidentiality of any API tokens or credentials you configure in the Extension</li>
            <li>Any content you export and how you use or share that content</li>
            <li>Backing up your exported data - we are not responsible for data loss</li>
            <li>Complying with all applicable laws and regulations when using the Extension</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            The Extension integrates with third-party services (Notion, Obsidian, etc.). Your use of these services is subject to their respective terms of service and privacy policies. We are not responsible for the practices or policies of these third-party services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Chat2Note is open source software. The source code and documentation are available under the terms specified in our repository. You retain all rights to the content you export using the Extension.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            THE EXTENSION IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, OR NON-INFRINGEMENT.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We do not guarantee that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>The Extension will be error-free or uninterrupted</li>
            <li>The Extension will be compatible with all versions of supported platforms</li>
            <li>Exported data will be complete or accurate in all cases</li>
            <li>The Extension will meet your specific requirements</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN NO EVENT SHALL CHAT2NOTE OR ITS CONTRIBUTORS BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS OR REVENUES, WHETHER INCURRED DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE LOSSES RESULTING FROM:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Your use or inability to use the Extension</li>
            <li>Any unauthorized access to or use of your data</li>
            <li>Any bugs, viruses, or other harmful components</li>
            <li>Any errors or omissions in exported content</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">9. Changes to Service</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the Extension (or any part thereof) at any time without notice. We will not be liable to you or any third party for any modification, suspension, or discontinuance of the Extension.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">10. Platform Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            AI chat platforms (ChatGPT, Claude, DeepSeek, Gemini, Kimi, Yuanbao, Doubao, Grok, etc.) may update their interfaces or APIs, which could affect the Extension's functionality. We will make reasonable efforts to maintain compatibility, but we cannot guarantee that the Extension will always work with the latest versions of these platforms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">11. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            You may stop using the Extension at any time by uninstalling it from your browser. These Terms will continue to apply to your prior use of the Extension.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify users of material changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of these Terms. Your continued use of the Extension after such changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">13. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which the maintainers are located, without regard to conflict of law principles.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">14. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@chat2note.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300 underline">support@chat2note.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">15. Severability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            If any provision of these Terms is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision will be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary so that these Terms will otherwise remain in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</LandingLayout>
